{
  "stem": "10588.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the last time I saw my family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother could have been alive, but she didn't want to abandon the children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Her [NON-ENGLISH] was tested.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I didn't know at the time what the right and the left-- because it was disguised-- a fraudulent-- [INAUDIBLE] which had a Red Cross sign on it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And all my life I knew Red Cross stands for help.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were promised to get help and better medication, so I was so glad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And also, they gave us the impression-- who is old, who is sick, who is pregnant, it's hard to work-- they're going to get all right.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I said, look, it doesn't even sound like the same Nazis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was grateful at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then, the worst part was when I found out-- since we didn't know-- I never said goodbye to any of them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one thing, everything that I loved and held sacred, everything was gone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My family-- that was the last day on earth for my family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Thousands of Jews from, from the ghetto of Nowe Miasto came together in the beginning of a living hell for me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we didn't know it yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They marched us in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And from the start, I lost freedom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were taken to a place where there's supposed to be-- told us we were going to take a bath.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was clutching a little photograph in my-- everything was thrown away but a little photograph from my family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The told me to give it to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I didn't want to, so I got beaten.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I realized later that I might get killed, so I gave away the last shred of my past.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They put on a tattoo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Mine was two, five, six, seven, three, which means that 25,673 people before me had those numbers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "However, those that they sent to the gas chamber, they didn't put on numbers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So what seemed a misfortune at that time-- found out I have a number.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The others didn't have numbers, but neither do they have life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And later, they shaved our hair, heads, and all hair in any private places.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "For the first time in my life-- I came from a home where I was very modest, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I wasn't wearing slacks at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I never undressed, even from my own parents in front, since when I was already little older, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And here you had to disrobe completely naked before strangers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Some girls had their monthly cycle and nothing to shield themselves with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then they shaved us all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "All of a sudden, our past was gone, everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we went into the shower.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We went to one place and went out to another.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There was a whole mountain of striped clothes, which was the lager. 'Lager' means camp-- concentration camp, except that was not a concentration.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It was a killing center where-- death factory, because I came to Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But there was Auschwitz, and there was Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And Birkenau had crematoriums and, and gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we were given those clothes, and we put on-- the same number that we had on the arm was sewn on here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "From then on, I was no longer Itka.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I became number two, five, six, seven, three.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Except-- each time they called my number, I was so angry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And under my breath, I would say-- under my breath, I used to say 'Itka.' Maybe to you, I'm a number, but I'm not.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I will never-- I cannot [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I'm Itka.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I remember distinctly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Each time when they said it, I said, no, I will never see myself through your eyes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And with each guard, they had in another pile, wooden clogs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Some were fortunate that they got a matching pair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I was not so fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I had an unmatched pair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And we got an enamel bowl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We were told if we lose the bowl or if we're going to use it for-- to relieve ourselves, we're not going to get another bowl.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "If they catch us relieving in it, we're going to get hit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I thought, what are they talking about?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who would want to relieve themself in a bowl that you're eating?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I didn't know the conditions of the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we walked out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we looked at each other, and we all looked the same.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From that, they brought us to our barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The barrack had bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Most of them had one blanket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some didn't even have a blanket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were three, three bunk beds like [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
